# NFS

## Installation

```bash
apt install nfs-kernel-server -y
```

## Configuration

```bash
nano /etc/exports
```

Exemple :

```bash
/srv/nfs/shared 192.168.1.0/24(rw,sync,no_subtree_check)
```

## Appliquer

```bash
exportfs -a
systemctl restart nfs-kernel-server
```

## Montage client

```bash
mount -t nfs 192.168.1.10:/srv/nfs/shared /mnt/nfs
```

