# SAMBA

## Installation

```bash
apt update
apt install samba samba-common-bin -y
```

## Sauvegarde config

```bash
cp /etc/samba/smb.conf /etc/samba/smb.conf.bak
```

## Créer le dossier partagé

```bash
mkdir -p /home/shared/partage
chown root:root /home/shared/partage
chmod 755 /home/shared/partage
```

## Ajouter un utilisateur Samba

```bash
smbpasswd -a user
```

## Configuration

```bash
nano /etc/samba/smb.conf
```

Exemple :

```bash
[Partage]
path = /home/shared/partage
valid users = user
read only = no
browseable = yes
inherit permissions = yes
```

## Chiffrement SMB

```bash
smb encrypt = mandatory
```

## Vérifier la config

```bash
testparm
```

## Redémarrer Samba

```bash
systemctl restart smbd
```

## Vérifier Samba

```bash
systemctl status smbd
```

## Pare-feu

```bash
ufw allow Samba
```

